  "texts": [
    "The preprocessed text is then examined to ensure that the quality of the data has not been lost.",
    "If it is deemed that the preprocessing is not satisfactory, appropriate steps are revised.",
    "The preprocessed technical text can now be used for a variety of tasks.",
    "There are several areas of PHM and maintenance that can benefit from TLP.",
    "With the help of domain experts and analysts, the areas where TLP will be effective can be identified, and appropriate computational resources can be procured."
